      "name": "Bangs.to",
      "alternateName": "bangs.to",
      "description": "Blazing-fast DuckDuckGo-style !bangs for your search engine. Redirects cached browser-side to avoid DNS latency. Privacy-first search engine shortcuts powered by a JavaScript Service Worker.",
